data.description: Enjoy peace and quiet in this gorgeous Beazer Home on an oversized lot in Southwinds,  boasting a brick exterior, luxury vinyl flooring, energy efficient features, and a covered patio. Master new recipes in the  kitchen, complete with quartz countertops, mosaic backsplash, stainless steel appliances, 42” upper cabinets, and pendant  lighting. With direct access to the Grand Parkway and I-10, commuters from Southwinds love the easy drive to Downtown  Houston and other major business areas. A variety of popular restaurants, shops, and beaches are only a short distance away.  Community comforts include a pool, recreation center, playground, and picnic area. Zoned to the Goose Creek CISD. This  could be your dream home – call now!
